{"tid":1637974,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加拒教英超：我是阿仙奴人","createTime":"2019-10-08T07:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T18:31:20.000Z","uid":153600,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"43705af8a0291c3ecd12ea0e1f50c68467afb5c6","tid":1637974,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】名帥雲加在前季離開執教了22年的阿仙奴後，一直未有重執教鞭，最近透露曾拒絕多家英超球會的邀請。<br />\n<br />\n今月將滿70歲的雲加（Arsene Wenger）自言仍然未決定下一份工作是甚麼：「我是阿仙奴人，除此之外，我是專業領隊，不能夠停止工作。我決定離開英超，因為跟兵工廠關係太深厚了。」<br />\n<br />\n「我曾經有機會於英格蘭工作，但一一拒絕了。我不希望告訴大家是哪些球會，因為他們現在都有主帥帶領，說出來對他們都不好不公平。」雲加續說。<br />\n<br />\n除了球會之外，國際足協亦向雲加拋出橄欖枝，曾自言比較喜歡領軍的他仍然在考慮當中：「那是世界足球發展的首長，我在不久的將來會作出決定。他們正尋找有豐富經驗、球賽知識的人出任。」<br />\n<br />\n爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7003c07981dabe75a964f7f44099dac06e187704","tid":1637974,"uid":69472,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:06:12.000Z","msg":"我迷雲呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ae815adb901032f0bc8b2f6a592579d14afbce","tid":1637974,"uid":13395,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"我係迷雲黨呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ff8b3116f8de1bf8d792922872bc9437fc6334","tid":1637974,"uid":153,"like":16,"dislike":32,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:11:31.000Z","msg":"無工開就無工開啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b3f487588c9202f48fcf7afebe52419ca7485c","tid":1637974,"uid":308486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺<img src